    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designates vertical enclosures in buildings containing a stairway and having a fire endurance rating high enough to qualify as fire escapes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
